sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant SE as /sprint-end
    participant FS as docs/sprints/
    participant Arch as docs/kanban-archive.md
    participant Co as ~/.claude/companies/[name]/retrospectives/

    H->>SE: /sprint-end

    note over SE: Phase 1 — AFK Draft
    SE->>FS: Read sprint-NN.md (goals + carry-in + deadlines)
    SE->>Arch: Read kanban (estimated vs actual token bands)
    SE->>FS: Draft sprint close section (velocity, completed, carry-over)
    SE->>FS: Update HANDOFF.md (Session type: Sprint Close)
    SE->>FS: Append velocity row to docs/metrics/metrics-log.md

    note over SE: Phase 2 — HITL Retro
    SE->>H: Present sprint summary + draft retro questions
    H->>SE: Retro responses (what went well / delta / actions)
    H->>SE: Confirm

    SE->>Arch: Write kanban-archive.md (estimated vs actual per ticket)
    SE->>FS: Complete sprint-NN.md (Sprint End section)
    SE->>Co: Save retrospectives/sprint-NN-retro.md

    SE->>H: Sprint token total surfaced
    SE->>H: Suggest /sprint-start for next sprint or /go-nogo if release approaching
